net.sourceforge.jaad.mp4.od

Class DecoderConfigDescriptor

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sourceforge.jaad.mp4.od.Descriptor
      • net.sourceforge.jaad.mp4.od.DecoderConfigDescriptor

  • public class DecoderConfigDescriptor
extends Descriptor
    The DecoderConfigDescriptor provides information about the decoder type and the required decoder resources needed for the associates elementary stream. This is needed at the receiver to determine whether it is able to decode the elementary stream. A stream type identifies the category of the stream while the optional decoder specific information contains stream specific information for the set up of the decoder in a stream specific format that is opaque to this layer.
